{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-18", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "從未懷疑，從未遠離", "storyInfo": "阿米婭藉助從黑王冠中得到的知識勉強拖延了普瑞賽斯的行動。眾人與博士的聯絡重新恢復，當務之急是化解普瑞賽斯與PRTS帶來的危機。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_drkcludsthdr", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "d"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 1.0, "channel": "d", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g13_rhodesdeck_origin", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_bat_act37d0d0_01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你尚且來不及思考剛剛發生的變故，凱爾希已經從你的視野中完全消失……"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甲板上只留下那件外套。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$Mon3tr_n"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（痛苦的嘶鳴）", "name": "Mon3tr"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緊隨凱爾希的消失，Mon3tr龐大的身軀也開始收縮，變成了一枚黑色的晶體狀的“繭”。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "AMa-10也曾是我得意的創造。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#2$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這並非我期待的結果。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#2$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "她有自己的名字。;她的名字是“凱爾希”。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line25", "option2": "line25"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1718_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它已經有了自己的代號，我並不認同再次命名的意義。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1718_1#3$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "普瑞賽斯走向留在甲板上的繭狀物體。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$3"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——博士，退後！我必須保護Mon3tr！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#6$3"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spelldfns_1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 255.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id